      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "A CONCURRENT RESOLUTION TO DESIGNATE THE MONTH OF JUNE 2026 AS \"FAMILY MONTH\" AND JOIN WITH THE CITIZENS OF SOUTH CAROLINA TO COMMEND THE NOBLE ENDEAVORS OF THOSE WHO SEEK TO PROTECT AND STRENGTHEN THE TRADITIONAL VALUES OF OUR STATE AND COUNTRY."
    }
